      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't let you down? This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a steady companion on many adventures! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional ride ready for its next owner. It's a great opportunity to get a dependable car at a very accessible price point!",
